PortSystem 1.0

name			fcrackzip
version			0.3
categories		security
platforms		darwin
maintainers		mww@opendarwin.org
description		Portable, fast and featureful ZIP password cracker
long_description	${description}

homepage		http://www.goof.com/pcg/marc/fcrackzip.html
